data.description: This one-story, waterfront home offers pretty sunset views for you to enjoy on your screened porch with in-ground spa. Located within the gated community of Lakefield, this home is close to the Winter Equestrian Festival and Wanderers Club. This property offers a split floor-plan for privacy. The master bedroom has an updated ensuite bathroom with separate bathtub and shower and two walk-in closets. Some of the upgrades include a brand new washer and dryer, newer ac (about 3 years old) and two renovated bathrooms. This is a lovely, family community located in Wellington's most-desired school district.
